message: The barbarity of the Israeli occupation didn't kill the innocent people of Gaza or bombed their homes only, but it also killed their simple dreams too! The owners of the demolished houses in Gaza due to the Israeli occupation terrorist attacks, are facing hard situations due to the extreme cold and the shortage of the daily life basics, the Israeli occupation prevents any help to build the homes in Gaza from entering it, even it prevents the basic needs too! Today they are homeless, living in caravans, suffering the spreading of diseases due to the poor health state in these caravans, our children don't have schools! The Israeli occupation monster destroyed them and destroyed the dreams of the children, it also restricts their lives and stop the building materials from entering Gaza to rebuild the schools! Our Palestinian children had been killed and displaced and became homeless, can you imagine the feeling of a helpless father that couldn't protect his children from the hatred of the Israeli occupation and couldn't offer the simplest life basics to them?! #enough_siege #BreakGazaSiege Watch these videos please: --------------
